---
import { Markdown, Partial } from '@splendidlabz/astro'
import NewsletterForm from '../../components/NewsletterForm.svelte'
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div
      class="grid-simple bp10:[--cols:9] items-center gap-x-[2rem] max-w-standard mx-auto"
    >
      <hgroup class="bp10:[--span:5] max-w-narrow mx-auto">
        <h2 class="h1 text-zred-500">Follow My Journey</h2>
        <p class="h1-subhead mt-2">
          <Markdown inline>
            If you're into making things and growing as a person, you'll
            probably feel at home here.
          </Markdown>
        </p>
      </hgroup>

      <div class="vertical bp10:[--span:5] max-w-narrow mx-auto">
        <div class="card card-red prose">
          <!-- prettier-ignore -->
          <Markdown>
            I share what I'm learning on this newsletter â€” code, building businesses, and living well. 

            Sometimes I write about technical deep-dives, product updates, musings on how to live, and sometimes my struggles and how I'm breaking through. 

            Regardless of the type of content, I do my best to send you an update every week. 
          </Markdown>

          <NewsletterForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-bp10:justify-self-center bp10:[--span:4]">
        <Partial path="LotoQuote" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
